text.tspan: Animation: Once dialog title is tapped, selection
dialog opens from top to bottom.
Specs for this icon are here for information purpose,
and must be ultimately defined in applications specs.
Once selection is done, dialog closes from bottom to
top and name of selection appears below the title.
Note that the design of the selection name
(here: ringtone 2) is yet to be defined.
